Description:
Riverfront Living at Its Best!
Riviere is a Riverfront Community set on the banks of the Yarra and, located under 4km from the CBD. Its living spaces are as beautiful as they are functional. Raw stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances, warehouse-style lighting and recycled timber are just some of the carefully selected interior features.
Apartment B302 further features:-
- intercom activated secure entry;
- a spacious and highly functional internal floorplan;
- queen-sized bedroom with ample mirrored built-in robe;
- second double bedroom/ideal guest room or home office with mirror-fronted robe;
- sleek and modern bathroom;
- smart Smeg kitchen appliances inc. ceramic cooktop and electric oven PLUS dishwasher;
- open kitchen / living offering direct access to the
- north-facing private balcony.
- single carparking for one (1) vehicle PLUS separate storage cage.
Further enjoy wall-mounted heat/cooling, hardwood boards to the living areas, wall-to-wall carpet to the bedrooms and quality window furnishings.
Step outside and the same careful attention to detail resonates. Rivières beautifully landscaped common area showcases the surrounding bushland and flows down to the Yarra River. This exceptionally beautiful stretch of the river overlooks Studley Park, Yarra Bend Park and Dights Falls and is also positioned just upstream from the Abbotsford Convent and the Collingwood Childrens farm.
Its no wonder that The Age newspaper nominated Trenerry Crescent as the best street in Abbotsford!
Current leased on a periodic basis to an A1 Tenant, returning $23, 988 per annum.
Internal area
66.2m²
